# Microsoft Clarity project ID (public — safe to expose client-side).
# Sign up free at https://clarity.microsoft.com, create a project for
# davessweater.com, and copy the Project ID from the tracking snippet it gives
# you. Without this set, the Clarity script is omitted entirely (fail-closed) —
# GA4 click tracking still works. Set the same value in Vercel → Settings →
# Environment Variables (Production + Preview) and in .env.local for local dev.
NEXT_PUBLIC_CLARITY_PROJECT_ID=
